OL,3,CHomeowner suing over mould hit with
OL,4,C#46k bill after law firm's collapse
OL,6,FA father-of-four who took legal action
OL,7,Fover his mouldy home was left with a
OL,8,F#46,000 bill when the no-win-no-fee
OL,9,Ffirm representing him collapsed.
OL,11,FWaqas, who asked not to be identified
OL,12,Fin full, appointed SSB Law after his
OL,13,Fhouse in Bradford developed a damp
OL,14,Fproblem thought to be linked to cavity
OL,15,Fwall insulation.
OL,17,FBut when the firm went bust in
OL,18,FJanuary, he was unexpectedly landed
OL,19,Fwith the legal costs relating to the
OL,20,Fcase.
