OL,6,FHe said the stress of the situation
OL,7,Fcaused his father to have a heart
OL,8,Fattack.
OL,10,F"I had to sell my wife's jewellery,
OL,11,Fget rid of my car, sell off my kids'
OL,12,Fjewellery, my father had to dip into
OL,13,Fhis pension pot," he said.
OL,15,F"I had to gather money from family
OL,16,Fmembers and friends to pay off that
OL,17,F#46,000."
OL,19,FWaqas had used money borrowed from his
OL,20,Ffather to buy his property.
