OL,6,F"It was embarrassing," he said. "One
OL,7,Fof my kids' beds is next to the window
OL,8,Fand the whole bed used to go (damp).
OL,9,FYou'd wake up in the morning to get
OL,10,Fclothes to wear and you couldn't wear
OL,11,Fit. The whole house would smell."
OL,13,FHe was among around 1,500 property
OL,14,Fowners using Sheffield-based SSB to
OL,15,Fmake a no-win-no-fee claim.
OL,17,FFollowing the firm's collapse, ex-
OL,18,Fclients are facing legal bills of
OL,19,F#35,000 on average.
