OL,6,FNaz Shah, MP for Bradford West, hosted
OL,7,Fa meeting for affected constituents.
OL,9,FShe said: "I think it's a national
OL,10,Fcrisis - I think it's national scandal.
OL,12,F"The stories we've heard from
OL,13,Fconstituents were so horrific. I
OL,14,Fdidn't realise the depth of it."
OL,16,FThe Solicitors' Regulation Authority
OL,17,Fis now investigating.
