OL,6,FFRP, the administrators for SSB Law,
OL,7,Fsaid: "While SSB is no longer trading,
OL,8,Fwe've secured the transition of all
OL,9,Flive case work to new providers and
OL,10,Fhave notified clients. We'll be
OL,11,Fmanaging that process over the coming
OL,12,Fweeks to ensure a smooth transition."
